data.description: Hidden gem in a secluded area of Palm Bay. Home is ready for immediate occupancy; seller has kept it in immaculate shape. Top of the line Bosch appliances, granite counters, speed queen commercial laundry, tankless water heater, large pantry, pool has stunning sunset views with upgraded pump and filter, screened in pool area, good size pool deck for entertaining. Resort like community, with tennis court, large community pool, clubhouse, fitness center. The community also has a walk path about 2.5 miles for your avid walkers.
